what am I thinking of?

166
00:07:30,522 --> 00:07:32,055
On the count of three.

167
00:07:32,124 --> 00:07:34,924
One, two, three.

168
00:07:34,993 --> 00:07:38,228
Robot monkey butler.
Robot monkey butler.

169
00:07:38,296 --> 00:07:40,096
Okay, good.

170
00:07:40,165 --> 00:07:43,466
Should I leave
you two alone?

171
00:07:43,535 --> 00:07:46,936
