high school football games.

178
00:08:03,722 --> 00:08:04,921
Sorry.

179
00:08:04,990 --> 00:08:06,734
You know, it doesn't matter,
nothing matters.

180
00:08:06,758 --> 00:08:08,491
Is there anything
I can do?

181
00:08:08,560 --> 00:08:10,493
