of losing it.

232
00:10:22,019 --> 00:10:23,952
Oh, boy.
He cared about this a lot.

233
00:10:24,021 --> 00:10:26,088
Yeah. What can we do
to help him?

234
00:10:26,156 --> 00:10:28,290
Well, grieving is a process.

235
00:10:28,359 --> 00:10:31,293
